

=Description=

"Quality Quids are:

* a fundraising community currency

* a loyalty system for community groups, co-ops, green businesses and the social economy at large

* a multiplier of wealth, creating a greater positive impact for every pound spent

* a tool for facilitating investment in social enterprises

* a currency for social enterprises to trade in on a mutual credit basis - increasing the levels of cooperation in the sector through creating a currency in which supply of low-cost credit is sufficient.

* a method of building a commons of natural resources (land etc.), productive assets (equiptment etc.) and infrastructure (eg. live/work space, wirelessNetworks, qualityQuids etc.). collectively owned and distributed by udoo members."
(http://wiki.uniteddiversity.com/qualityquids)


